             was indicted for <rs id="t18030914-14-off83" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18030914-14-off83" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18030914-14-off83" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18030914-14-cd84" type="crimeDate">27th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030914-14-off83 t18030914-14-cd84"></join>, a handkerchief, value 2s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18030914-14-victim157" type="victimName">
                           Lewis 
